{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow people who require Epi-Pens to serve in the armed forces",
        "additional_details": "We believe that with proper training, access to necessary medical supplies, and reasonable accommodations, individuals with severe allergies can serve safely and effectively in various roles within the Armed Forces.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to allow individuals who require adrenaline auto-injectors due to severe allergies to be allowed to join the UK armed forces, provided they meet all other physical and mental health standards and can demonstrate effective management of their condition. ",
